description:
Thursday 4/19 - Today on the show we had Keke Palmer stop by where she spoke about dealing with anxiety, Trey Songz, new projects and more. Also, since Angela is still on vacation DJ Envy and Charlamagne took over "Ask Yee" with "Ask C & E ". Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man who attached his attached his home address to a note he passed to a bank teller demanding money.
